name: Silver Phosphenes
description:
Cyberspace Series

Created by Fivos Doganis (@fdoganis), inspired by the alterations of the human mind and body described in William Gibson's Neuromancer.

"And in the bloodlit dark behind his eyes, silver phosphenes boiling in from the edge of space, hypnagogic images jerking past like film compiled from random frames."
William Gibson, Neuromancer (Sprawl, #1)
